        {
            "title": "阿斯利康股價下跌,FDA專家小組否決乳癌藥物camizestrant",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"410\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/GtKneRkHTHKMYgJTDfJwvg--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTYwNg--/https://i-invdn-com.investing.com/news/asian_2_M_1440047814.jpg\" width=\"650\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Investing.com - 阿斯利康股價週四下跌,此前美國食品藥物管理局外部專家小組投票反對支持該公司實驗性乳癌治療藥物camizestrant的風險效益評估。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">截至格林威治標準時間07:37,該股在倫敦下跌1.6%。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">FDA腫瘤藥物諮詢委員會以6票對3票否決了這款口服藥物,阿斯利康正在開發該藥物作為由特定基因突變驅動的一種乳癌的一線治療方法。該小組認為,對於在現有療法下疾病未惡化的患者而言,該藥物未能顯示出\"有意義的益處\"。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-c329f541-5634-3a96-aa34-fd804a5193bc-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">雖然諮詢小組的投票不具約束力,但FDA通常會遵循其建議。該機構的最終決定預計將於稍後公布。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">摩根士丹利分析師Sarita Kapila領導的團隊表示,這一決定造成了\"監管不確定性並打擊了投資者信心\"。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">他們指出:\"在6比3的ODAC負面投票之後,我們認為在SERENA-6適應症中獲得批准的可能性降低,儘管仍有可能獲得批准。\"</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">阿斯利康表示對這一結果感到\"失望\",但對其試驗結果以及該藥物對患者的潛在益處充滿信心。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">在臨床試驗中,camizestrant將疾病惡化時間延遲了超過6個月。與其他抗癌藥物聯合使用時,患者的中位無惡化生存期為16個月,而接受現有標準治療的患者為9.2個月。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><br/></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><em>此文章由人工智能協助翻譯。更多資訊，請參閱我們的使用條款。</em></p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E9%98%BF%E6%96%AF%E5%88%A9%E5%BA%B7%E8%82%A1%E5%83%B9%E4%B8%8B%E8%B7%8C-fda%E5%B0%88%E5%AE%B6%E5%B0%8F%E7%B5%84%E5%90%A6%E6%B1%BA%E4%B9%B3%E7%99%8C%E8%97%A5%E7%89%A9camizestrant-083640881.html",
