        },
        {
            "title": "華爾街投行薪資曝！高盛非最高、頂級分析師年薪破27萬美元但「代價驚人」",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"214\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/kpfO1LhT4bOSD5lThZHh2A--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTcwNTtoPTM5Nw--/https://media.zenfs.com/ca/cnyes_hk_559/0de7ade9e311a1ddf740b1a3c774f145\" width=\"380\"/></div></figure></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E8%8F%AF%E7%88%BE%E8%A1%97%E6%8A%95%E8%A1%8C%E8%96%AA%E8%B3%87%E6%9B%9D-%E9%AB%98%E7%9B%9B%E9%9D%9E%E6%9C%80%E9%AB%98-%E9%A0%82%E7%B4%9A%E5%88%86%E6%9E%90%E5%B8%AB%E5%B9%B4%E8%96%AA%E7%A0%B427%E8%90%AC%E7%BE%8E%E5%85%83%E4%BD%86-%E4%BB%A3%E5%83%B9%E9%A9%9A%E4%BA%BA-074016482.html",
